# Blog images — Option A (mandatory when this rule applies)

You are editing blog images or `src/data/blog/**` posts. **Follow this before changing assets or § captions.**

## Structure

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `{slug}-hero.webp` | `ogImage` + page hero — **§1 scene** (e.g. Tsutaya sign). No identifiable faces. |
| `{slug}-1.webp` | **One** body `![]()` — proof for **one section** (e.g. §3 hokoten, Yamano on the **left**). |

- `md5(hero) ≠ md5(body)`. WebP ~1200px, q~80–82.

## Never (anti-pattern `626a226`)

- Auto-pick from `Downloads` / recent files (couple selfie, indoor Tokyo Tower, etc.)
- Same file for hero and body
- Wide **pixel mosaic** or heavy blur over buildings/signs
- Caption says blur/mosaic but body still mentions 「표정」「사진 왼쪽」/ expressions / 写真の左側

## Privacy (body photo)

- **Gaussian blur only**, light — **crowd silhouettes stay visible**
- Blur **lower / people zone only**; Yamano, Mitsukoshi, streetscape stay sharp
- User said 「이 정도면 충분」→ do **not** strengthen blur

## Photo selection

- Use **user-attached photos** or **user-specified folder only**
- Propose hero vs body vs reject table before replacing files

## Text (ko / en / ja together)

- Captions: face **blur** (not mosaic): KO 블러, EN softly blurred, JA ぼかし
- Yamano land price: **6,710万 yen/m² (2026), 20 consecutive years** (not 21)

## Before “done”

- [ ] hero ≠ body, hero not a personal selfie
- [ ] body matches §3 geography (Yamano left if stated)
- [ ] 3 locales consistent with edit
- [ ] No git push unless user asks

Before edits: read repo `BLOG_IMAGE_RULES_1PAGE.md` and AG Knowledge **`gsf_blog_image_option_a`** (see `AGENTS.md`).
